data.text:
From the biggest festival to the smallest church social, Kenny Smyth delivers porta-loos to them all.

Part philosopher, part comedian and all heart, Kenny is one of the cogs in society’s machinery; a knight in shining overalls taking care of business with his faithful 'Splashdown crew'.

The film lifts the lid on one of Australia’s roughest diamonds KENNY as he juggles family tensions, fatherhood and sewage with charm, humour and unflinching dignity.
